      'Data privacy statement'
      '------------------------'
      ''
      'Contact Person'
      '-----------------'
      'Contact person for any data privacy issues of the astronomy program ''Albireo Astronomy Toolbox'' is:'
      ''
      'Frank Szemkus'
      'eMail-Address: kontakt@stecknitz-astronomie.de'
      ''
      ''
      'What kind of personal data are collected'
      '-------------------------------------------'
      'The Software Albireo Astronomy Toolbox, which you can download under www.stecknitz-astronomie.de'
      'needs your year of birth and your place of location as a local dataset.'
      'The dataset is stored on you local computer. A transfer of this data takes not place.'
      'The year of birth is needed to calculate telsecope capablites. The place ot location is needed to calculate'
      'the local view if the starry sky.'
      ''
      'A connection to the site www.stecknitz-astronomie.de will be opened, using the default internet browser, if you press'
      '- the donation button'
      '- Help-Labels  in dialogue ''Info'''
      'For this case personal data in terms of your IP-address can be transmitted to the site'
      'www.stecknitz-astronomie.de.'
      ''
      'If you need more information about the privacy statment of  www.stecknitz-astronomie.de please'
      'go to site  https://www.stecknitz-astronomie.de/datenschutzerklaerung/.'
    )
    TabOrder = 1
  end
